  <name>Spearmint</name>
  <summary>Free and open-source Quake 3 based engine</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Spearmint is a heavily modified version of the Quake III Arena engine. It has various visual enhancements, bug fixes, and local splitscreen multiplayer.
    </p>
    <p>
      Spearmint is not compatible with Quake III Arena servers, mods (the QVM/DLL files), or demos (game recordings).
    </p>
